  "detailed_description": "A terrible plane crash took the lives of all the passengers and crew... except one. You have survived in the middle of the boundless ocean and now you have to challenge fate and fight for your life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.poster.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.webm?t=1768654017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.mp4?t=1768654017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create, Build, and Expand Your Raft!</h2><br>With over 60 different types of useful crafting and building options, you can build a new home right in the middle of the ocean!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/622ce68ee22af62d8ab2b4ee4e75bdc2.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer - Play Online!</h2><br>Gather resources, expand your raft, and help each other survive in this boundless and dangerous ocean. Teamwork is your key to survival!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/eb3456d52881fbe4cbc1484ffb8fb870.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Customization</h2><br>Hundreds of clothing and accessories help you express your individuality and stand out from your team. Survive in style!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/d379473cf3d65423279b67192130e28c.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Island Adventures</h2><br>Ten unique islands await you with their own dangers, mysteries, and valuable treasures. But before you set sail, don't forget to stock up on weapons and provisions. Adventures await you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/eb96ce12e51bdd64b9c583d0db94a212.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/f547928972eb85361324387a87294c91.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wandering Merchant</h2><br>A lone wanderer will gladly share interesting stories from his travels, give you useful advice, and exchange your resources for blueprints of new buildings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ef456926d2bc49a66337ea7122a60f0b.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/bb0ede136b7080b39e78271f6bfbc5af.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Some banners are rendered and modified with help of 3d model by Julian Johnson-Mortimer.",
  "about_the_game": "A terrible plane crash took the lives of all the passengers and crew... except one. You have survived in the middle of the boundless ocean and now you have to challenge fate and fight for your life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.poster.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.webm?t=1768654017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ad7ab5d1446d8da688923a39d2f3ad01.mp4?t=1768654017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create, Build, and Expand Your Raft!</h2><br>With over 60 different types of useful crafting and building options, you can build a new home right in the middle of the ocean!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/622ce68ee22af62d8ab2b4ee4e75bdc2.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer - Play Online!</h2><br>Gather resources, expand your raft, and help each other survive in this boundless and dangerous ocean. Teamwork is your key to survival!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/eb3456d52881fbe4cbc1484ffb8fb870.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Customization</h2><br>Hundreds of clothing and accessories help you express your individuality and stand out from your team. Survive in style!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/d379473cf3d65423279b67192130e28c.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Island Adventures</h2><br>Ten unique islands await you with their own dangers, mysteries, and valuable treasures. But before you set sail, don't forget to stock up on weapons and provisions. Adventures await you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/eb96ce12e51bdd64b9c583d0db94a212.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/f547928972eb85361324387a87294c91.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wandering Merchant</h2><br>A lone wanderer will gladly share interesting stories from his travels, give you useful advice, and exchange your resources for blueprints of new buildings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/ef456926d2bc49a66337ea7122a60f0b.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094000/extras/bb0ede136b7080b39e78271f6bfbc5af.avif?t=1768654017\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Some banners are rendered and modified with help of 3d model by Julian Johnson-Mortimer.",
